Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.55,0:00:09.01,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}I had lost my way during my journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.01,0:00:17.02,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Only my soul was wandering, while I stood still.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.02,0:00:25.28,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}But right now, I'm walking to a distant place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.28,0:00:33.53,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}That's right, ever since I met you on this road.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.62,0:00:41.96,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}The travellers witnessed the song, the forbidden song,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.96,0:00:52.72,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}And I became attached to it as I heard it alone with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.72,0:01:00.81,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}If the world I saw in my dreams exists somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.81,0:01:09.20,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Let's go search for it, beyond the winds.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.20,0:01:13.37,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Whether it's a freezing dawn,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.37,0:01:17.58,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}A dry midday,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.58,0:01:21.75,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}A shivering night,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.75,0:01:28.00,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}or the ends of the Earth, let's go and see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.79,0:01:35.08,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Once upon a time in a village,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.08,0:01:39.03,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,an abundance of wheat would ripen and sway in the wind,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.03,0:01:42.50,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,and a wolf could be seen running through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.50,0:01:46.41,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Wheat that fell due to the wind would be trampled on by the wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.41,0:01:49.51,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,When the crop was poor, the wolf would then eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.64,0:01:53.62,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There was nothing in the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.62,0:01:55.69,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There was only warmth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.04,0:02:00.02,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, a promise was made.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.06,0:02:20.70,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Meetings and partings continued.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.70,0:02:26.44,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually, humans gained wealth using their own power.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.99,0:02:32.47,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There was probably no need to keep the promise faithfully anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.24,0:02:37.26,Chapter Name Title Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Wolf and Best Clothes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.23,0:02:43.23,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting awfully tired of these countryside roads.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.92,0:02:44.73,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.31,0:02:50.36,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a peddler?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.91,0:02:55.37,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If you head south for half a day, there's a small village in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.37,0:02:57.50,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I just came back from selling salt there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.50,0:02:59.12,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,So, all of that's salt?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.12,0:02:59.83,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.94,0:03:03.08,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,This is fur.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.32,0:03:07.79,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a stack of wheat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.79,0:03:10.80,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's strong in the heat and cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.82,0:03:12.80,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.50,0:03:15.85,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Since when has it become this daunting?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.85,0:03:20.36,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Truth be told, a pagan festival is about to start in a village to the south.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.36,0:03:21.41,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Pagan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.14,0:03:25.32,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't believe in the one and absolute God.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.32,0:03:27.15,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They're an outrageous folk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.15,0:03:31.69,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I think the law enforcement should use their power more like they did in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.69,0:03:33.65,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems they're just not as devoted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.65,0:03:36.95,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The pagans are probably using some cheap trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.95,0:03:38.50,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Pagans, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.37,0:03:41.32,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The people of Pasroe?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.70,0:03:46.17,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Lawrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.17,0:03:48.50,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, I'm really surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.50,0:03:51.50,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think there was a different method for harvesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:53.00,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to the Count.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:55.68,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't rely on the wolf anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.68,0:03:58.92,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, we can't say bad things. It's a god, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.02,0:04:02.39,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Lawrence!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.94,0:04:05.25,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello! It's been such a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.25,0:04:07.69,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, you came at a really great time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.69,0:04:09.94,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow is the harvest festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.94,0:04:14.44,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow? I thought it had already begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.99,0:04:16.99,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, we're just a bit ahead here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.99,0:04:17.70,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,How about a cup?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.70,0:04:21.78,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, don't drag Lawrence into this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:24.25,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, forgive my rudeness!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.68,0:04:28.34,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, do you know where Chloe is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.34,0:04:29.58,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Chloe?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:31.77,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so that's what it's about, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.77,0:04:33.95,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she's just my merchant apprentice, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.95,0:04:35.59,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought we'd have a drink
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.09,0:04:37.93,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,and talk about trade while we were at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.93,0:04:39.71,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.60,0:04:43.35,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That place is the final spot for the harvest this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.35,0:04:46.35,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,She might be the one to become Horo for the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.35,0:04:52.27,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there! That's where the wolf lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.81,0:04:56.54,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,So who's going to catch the wolf in the end? Just who? Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:04:59.63,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Chloe!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.78,0:05:02.70,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Lawrence!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.65,0:05:04.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You came!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.72,0:05:07.41,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Horo will escape if you look away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.83,0:05:10.67,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the last stack of wheat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.67,0:05:12.93,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Did your greed hide the wheat stack?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.93,0:05:15.22,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Check it well, or Horo will escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.22,0:05:17.42,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,So, who caught the wolf? Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:19.73,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It was Chloe! Chloe! Chloe!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.12,0:05:45.62,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Horo the wolf appeared! Catch her! Catch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.62,0:05:47.07,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,She headed that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:49.22,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch her, Lawrence!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.57,0:05:58.47,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, so treat me tonight, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.31,0:06:08.23,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "treat me tonight?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.86,0:06:16.57,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be in there for a week!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.36,0:06:22.66,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, a new trade route has opened up for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.85,0:06:28.08,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like Chloe's doing well as the village's merchant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.08,0:06:31.24,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, she's doing really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.24,0:06:33.08,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,This village will continue to prosper.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.15,0:06:36.90,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Thoreni silver coins?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.90,0:06:38.96,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen these in this area, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:43.89,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We can say goodbye to those dark, rusty silver coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.89,0:06:47.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll see the day when we rub shoulders with people in the big city soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.72,0:06:49.82,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we still have a long way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.82,0:06:55.89,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to the new feudal lord, Count Eirin Dotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.89,0:06:59.05,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to pray to the wolf anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.05,0:07:03.76,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We can overcome droughts and storms thanks to our own abilities now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.76,0:07:09.16,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than Thoreni silver coins, we'll be making Rumio gold coins!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.69,0:07:12.42,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope for your patronage when that time comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.33,0:07:30.65,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Outsiders will just be treated as a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:36.81,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, talking about Rumio gold coins is taking it too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.74,0:07:41.94,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.33,0:07:43.22,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'll sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.79,0:08:12.73,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be real.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.46,0:08:16.80,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.80,0:08:17.68,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.99,0:08:28.73,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.73,0:08:30.58,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing in my wagon?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.47,0:08:40.54,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.46,0:08:43.05,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Ea-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.03,0:08:44.98,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Ears?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.03,0:09:12.35,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.49,0:09:39.94,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pleasant moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.05,0:09:44.15,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any beer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.78,0:09:48.97,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't have anything like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.97,0:09:49.66,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,In the first place-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:53.22,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Then how about some food?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.03,0:09:56.52,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? What a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.17,0:10:06.92,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you some kind of possessing demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.50,0:10:09.93,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,How ungrateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.89,0:10:12.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you point your knife at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.72,0:10:15.28,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.28,0:10:18.73,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, you're not part of the local village.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.27,0:10:21.31,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, please forget what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.29,0:10:30.24,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Horo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.24,0:10:32.80,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while since I last took this form.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.64,0:10:35.80,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems it went well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.80,0:10:36.56,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Horo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.25,0:10:38.75,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's a good name, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.75,0:10:40.37,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.37,0:10:43.25,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I know something that goes by that name as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.49,0:10:48.46,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know of anyone named Horo, other than myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.46,0:10:50.01,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is that person?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:54.04,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the name of the god in a village from this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.04,0:10:57.05,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling me you're a god?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.49,0:11:03.71,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been called a god for a long time since I was bound to this land.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.71,0:11:06.37,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not as great as a real god.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.10,0:11:09.28,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I am nothing but Horo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.44,0:11:13.63,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,"She's a girl that's been locked up since she was small, and
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.63,0:11:16.33,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,she's strange and pathetic,"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.91,0:11:18.12,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,is probably what you're thinking, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.77,0:11:22.12,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I was born in the far North.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:23.44,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,North?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.44,0:11:26.63,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the summers are short and the winters are long.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.71,0:11:30.51,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,A forest in the country of Yoitsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.67,0:11:35.90,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a world where everything sparkled a brilliant silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.74,0:11:45.85,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a travelling merchant, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.48,0:11:48.86,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you take me with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.86,0:11:50.69,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.69,0:11:52.90,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a good eye for people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.54,0:11:58.93,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not a cold person who can nonchalantly refuse a person's request, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.93,0:12:00.32,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lean on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.32,0:12:01.62,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not that good of a person!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.62,0:12:03.37,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you treat me nicely?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.94,0:12:06.58,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just too cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.95,0:12:13.23,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't dislike this form, but it's too cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.83,0:12:22.76,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Horo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.90,0:12:28.44,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're really Kenrou Horo, then prove it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.52,0:12:33.41,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying you want to see my wolf form?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.41,0:12:33.99,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.33,0:12:36.53,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.53,0:12:38.63,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.63,0:12:40.41,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What about {\i1}you{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.38,0:12:45.79,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're a human, then I'll take you to a church and exorcise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.79,0:12:48.13,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Possessing demons cause great trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.59,0:12:52.96,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you're really the Horo who brings an abundant harvest, then I'll think it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:56.58,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You look like you could bring me great fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.13,0:13:02.89,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really want to see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.75,0:13:05.05,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.08,0:13:08.30,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask you one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.30,0:13:10.44,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you {\i1}really {\i0}want to see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.01,0:13:12.07,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}really {\i0}want to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.15,0:13:18.82,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless of the form, I can't change unless a price is paid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.13,0:13:20.78,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,In my case,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.78,0:13:22.19,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,it's blood from the living,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.97,0:13:24.70,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,or a bit of wheat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.53,0:13:26.97,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Take some of the wheat over there, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.79,0:13:42.76,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.31,0:13:46.93,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.35,0:14:08.97,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for my sudden return.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.97,0:14:10.09,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.09,0:14:13.92,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be heading towards the festival, but you can stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.03,0:14:21.77,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.77,0:14:22.34,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Horo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.84,0:14:23.64,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Horo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.15,0:14:29.58,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't bother showing up, so I had to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.25,0:14:33.38,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have to be in the grain barn?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.38,0:14:36.11,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Horo probably doesn't exist, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.63,0:14:38.40,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.40,0:14:39.80,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.80,0:14:41.49,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You promised you'd treat me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.12,0:14:44.11,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You smell differently from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.11,0:14:45.99,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you pass by Zauchebache?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.49,0:14:48.03,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a good sense of smell, as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.03,0:14:52.35,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The smell of the soil and life there just sticks to you naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.35,0:14:54.42,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Your look has changed, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.42,0:14:56.00,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's overflowing with confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.00,0:14:57.69,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.69,0:14:59.38,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels great.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:02.85,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I just might surpass you, one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.86,0:15:07.22,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to ask for your patronage when that happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.22,0:15:10.55,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,How mean! You probably don't think that way at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.55,0:15:11.89,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.89,0:15:13.60,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,This beer is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.77,0:15:18.50,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.50,0:15:21.38,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If you start believing in me, then I have a good proposal for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.49,0:15:26.66,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If it goes well, we can open up our own store, and even build our own house!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.52,0:15:29.70,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.17,0:15:31.37,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, take me seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.94,0:15:35.96,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a big business negotiation, and we can make a killing off it if it comes together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.79,0:15:39.81,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Lawrence?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.35,0:15:45.31,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really starting to look like your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.31,0:15:48.74,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father also had a good business sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.41,0:15:51.43,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that, this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.43,0:15:54.09,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm telling you all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:15:57.94,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There are always some strings attached to these big proposals.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.73,0:16:00.99,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that why you want to hire me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.73,0:16:06.73,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to partner up with you {\i1}because{\i0} I admire you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.73,0:16:11.76,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always taken everything you've told me to heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.76,0:16:14.31,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that I've gotten this far because of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.07,0:16:16.33,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.59,0:16:23.84,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.63,0:16:26.01,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.36,0:16:28.85,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still young.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.54,0:16:34.50,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than betting on this proposal, it'd be better if you gained more experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.26,0:16:38.70,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,How boring!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.70,0:16:41.11,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a chance for us to gain a profit together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.55,0:16:44.70,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring you some better proposals that are less dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.57,0:16:47.25,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll partner up with you on those.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.19,0:16:52.04,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I've grown without you even noticing, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.10,0:16:59.63,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you have a long way to go as a merchant.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.58,0:17:04.17,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have it coming when you underestimate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.81,0:17:08.68,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Experiencing something like that might be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.39,0:17:10.31,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.14,0:17:13.22,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You looked up to the sky for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.63,0:17:15.38,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find a good partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.38,0:17:16.48,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.96,0:17:19.36,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just imagining how it'd be if Horo were my partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.36,0:17:20.11,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Horo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.73,0:17:22.09,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.09,0:17:24.65,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I mean the real Horo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.65,0:17:27.93,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it, you were having delusions like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.93,0:17:29.23,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Delusions, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.23,0:17:30.91,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, delusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.91,0:17:32.32,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Delusions, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.32,0:17:33.41,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Delusions for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.68,0:17:37.37,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What if Horo actually existed?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.06,0:17:39.38,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Another delusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.38,0:17:40.88,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she's had painful times, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.26,0:17:43.24,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.24,0:17:45.26,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Horo is a god, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.90,0:17:47.42,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.85,0:18:02.58,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess there's no way she'd be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.71,0:18:05.64,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Whom are you seeking?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.25,0:18:07.22,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Horo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.22,0:18:09.45,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to act so surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.49,0:18:14.87,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Where were you hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.33,0:18:18.87,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,During this season, I live inside harvested wheat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.26,0:18:21.32,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I can never escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.32,0:18:22.79,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because someone is looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.20,0:18:24.60,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But, there's an exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.17,0:18:25.79,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Exception?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.80,0:18:30.82,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's a bigger stack of wheat than the one that was harvested last,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.82,0:18:32.76,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I can move to that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.54,0:18:35.92,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.84,0:18:41.19,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,How do I say it... I guess I can call you my savior.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.19,0:18:42.40,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You are my savior.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.28,0:18:44.56,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,During that time,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.27,0:18:47.65,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,when I saw your true form,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.17,0:18:50.40,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I was unusually surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.49,0:19:04.83,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that why you vanished?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.99,0:19:09.30,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.69,0:19:12.84,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I was asked for a favor by a young man a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.24,0:19:16.35,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I was asked to ripen the wheat for the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.70,0:19:19.27,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Since then, I've been protecting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.27,0:19:22.77,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,However, if abundant harvests repeat, it puts pressure on the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.77,0:19:25.14,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I had to let the land rest sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.77,0:19:29.86,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the villagers would say it was my whim that did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.32,0:19:33.11,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been getting worse these past years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.57,0:19:36.35,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No one needs me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.35,0:19:41.07,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever I'm needed, they run away scared when they see my true form.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.07,0:19:42.62,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even get close to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.80,0:19:47.63,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't what I had wished for.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.22,0:19:56.44,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, I'll believe that story.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.44,0:19:59.09,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a distrustful man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.09,0:20:02.46,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a place you want to go, once you leave the village?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.24,0:20:09.06,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to return to the North.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.64,0:20:25.76,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Lawrence?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.68,0:20:36.26,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, you can come out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.30,0:20:43.85,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It was quite hard to tie up my shoelaces in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.26,0:20:47.83,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.83,0:20:48.73,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoelaces?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.47,0:20:56.38,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is that my...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.04,0:20:58.66,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, does it look good?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.29,0:21:01.69,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are my best clothes; they took ten years to obtain!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.69,0:21:02.74,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.74,0:21:05.00,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The tailoring is quite good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.00,0:21:08.37,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a pretty good merchant.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.37,0:21:11.17,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Take those clothes off right now, or get off.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.17,0:21:12.67,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.92,0:21:15.57,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have it coming if you underestimate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.68,0:21:19.63,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'm counting on you, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.63,0:21:20.43,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Lawrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.26,0:21:22.81,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Craft, Lawrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.53,0:21:25.12,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Lawrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.12,0:21:30.81,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,In the future, your name shall be in my tales for eternity!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.81,0:21:33.74,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you don't need to talk about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.74,0:21:35.90,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Get your own meals, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.60,0:21:38.49,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not in an easy business.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.49,0:21:42.89,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not such a fool to think that I'd get free meals just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.90,0:21:48.04,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Horo Kenrou, the prideful wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.99,0:21:51.02,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.63,0:21:53.78,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bit confined.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.78,0:21:55.00,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen here...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.00,0:21:57.97,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it'll be a good way for me to get used to the cold.
Comment: 0,0:22:05.97,0:22:23.19,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.19,0:22:20.17,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven apples on the witch's tree
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.17,0:22:25.55,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,With seven seeds to plant inside of me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.55,0:22:30.73,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,In spring time I grew a magic song
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.73,0:22:33.47,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Then skipping along,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.47,0:22:36.03,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,I sang the song to everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.03,0:22:41.46,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,I look at the world through apple eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.46,0:22:46.79,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,And cut myself a slice of sunshine pie
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.79,0:22:52.13,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,I danced with the peanuts for the flies
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.13,0:22:54.76,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Till someone had told me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.76,0:22:57.82,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,To say hello for every good-bye
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.82,0:23:02.78,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Saw some sugar stars
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.78,0:23:07.87,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put them in a jar
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.87,0:23:10.44,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,And we'll wish around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.44,0:23:13.88,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh we'll wish around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.88,0:23:17.74,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a little wolf inside a cart
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.74,0:23:19.09,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,You say,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.09,0:23:23.38,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,And off I go from June to May
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.38,0:23:29.27,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh we'll wish around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.27,0:23:32.92,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's wish around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.88,0:23:43.90,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, Wolf and Distant Past.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.00,0:23:49.00,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, Wolf and Distant Past.
